---
title: Tip-top THIS™ Isn't Pork Sausages and Cheesy Chips with Homemade Onion Gravy and Buttery Peas
description: Perfectly pleasing, these vegetarian sausages swim in a bath of easy homemade onion gravy for a savoury sensation. Paired with crispy, cheesy chips and a side of peas, this is British comfort food that the whole family can enjoy.
